@page "/"

<PageTitle>Lesson 22</PageTitle>

<h1>Lesson 22 - Forms and Data Binding in Blazor</h1>

<p>
By the end of this lesson, you will be able to:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Build forms in Blazor using EditForm</li>
    <li>Use InputText, InputNumber, InputDate, and ValidationMessage</li>
    <li>Bind data with @@bind to keep UI and model values in sync</li>
    <li>Add validation using DataAnnotations (e.g., [Required], [Range])</li>
    <li>Handle form submission using OnValidSubmit</li>
    <li>Display validation summaries and field-level messages</li>
</ul>
